Package students

Class Student

java.lang.Object
students.Student
public class Student
extends java.lang.Object
This class represents a Student from any school. It contains all of the courses assigned to that specific student. It also contains all of the documents and assignments to allow giving a full summary of all the courses. It holds all of the calendar events associated to the student.

    • assignCalendarEvent

      public void assignCalendarEvent​(CalendarEvent event)
      This method adds the corresponding CalendarEvent object to the calendar. Note: If the event received has already passed, it will not add it. It allows a maximum of 24 hours since the event can still be today but at midnight and might still be relevant.
      Parameters:
      event - Calendar Event to be added
